race.comment: MILWAUKEE JACK (7) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. Recorded a nose win (17.84) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Rates a leading player. TRUE PROMISES (3) missed the frame last time, finishing 6th (19.08) last time in a Grade 5 at Richmond. Has won here at this journey. Worth following up. VALTERI BOY (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 324m behind Zipping Barclay (18.41) in a Grade 5. Great chance to atone. BIG SHOT (2) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.
